metadata.name: City of minimalism
metadata.description:
This art is represented by minimal representation and color, with varying widths, heights, and patterns. It has various building types and unique imagination city feeling.

This collection is unique by adding repeated pattern textures to simple expressions. The collection contains the emotions of various people, including themselves, family, friends, and children.
Depending on your emotional state, you will feel sadness, hope, joy, and comfort.

I hope you feel minimalism.

Dotory Minimal 2023
